after each sentence

*Imaš* li vremena? (Do you have time?)
On *imaš* priliku da postaneš uspešan. (You have an opportunity to become successful.)
*Imaš* li brata? (Do you have a brother?)
Koliko *imaš* godina? (How old are you?)
*Imaš* li nešto da kažeš? (Do you have anything to say?)
Uglavnom, *imaš* ono što si želiš. (Basically, you have what you want.)